description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, global CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by creating a root and rendering the App component within React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components in the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root container.
